lead_paragraph: FISHER--Jerome. Congregation Emanu-El of the City of New York records with deep sorrow the death of our cherished member, Jerome "Jack" Fisher. To his family and loved ones we express our profound sympathy. The beautiful qualities of his life shall endure forever. 1/3
